channel.title: Funniest game quotes you've ever heard?
channel.description:
Personally, I think a lot of quotes from San Andreas were really funny, like: "When I find that Chihuahua I'm gonna kill it!" "I had a dream and it died in San Andreas." "I smoke 'cause it gives me knowledge!"
What are yours? :retard:
